    Pipeline.PipelineVisitor

    public class PipelineTranslatorStreaming
extends PipelineTranslator
    PipelineTranslator for executing a Pipeline in Spark in streaming mode. This contains only the components specific to streaming: registry of streaming TransformTranslator and registry lookup code.
